NK101(de)005:1: // byang chub sems kyi don bsgom pa'i yi ge gzhi
NK101(de)005:2: lam 'bras bu'i don bsam pa zhes bya ba blta
NK101(de)005:3: bsgom spyod pa'i man ngag bzhugs so //
NK101(de)005:4: na mo mah+aa gu ru badz+ra d+hari d+har+m+ma r+aa dz+aa ya /
NK101(de)005:5: yongs rdzogs bshes gnyen 'dus pa'i dbus na mkhas //
NK101(de)005:6: nyes ltung dri bral 'dul 'dzin khrod na btsun //
NK101(de)005:7: yang dag rtogs pas grub pa'i nang na bzang //
NK101(de)005:8: bstan pa'i srog shing bla chen chos rje mkhyen //
NK101(de)005:9: chos kyi phung po brgya khri bzhi stong las //
NK101(de)005:10: sems kyis gsang 'di rig par ma gyur na //
NK101(de)005:11: ji ltar 'bad kyang don med ngal bar zad //
NK101(de)005:12: de phyir zab mo'i gtam gyis skabs dabye'o //
NK101(de)005:13: 'dir yang dag pa'i gnas lugs rtogs par 'dod pas ni //
NK101(de)005:14: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don khong du chud dgos la //
NK101(de)005:15: dang po gzhi ni rang gi sems stong pa yin min yod med gang du yang ma grub pa /
NK101(de)005:16: gzhan las ma byung bas rang byung /
NK101(de)005:17: til la mar bzhin du 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pa /
NK101(de)005:18: 'adi'o zhes brjod du mi nus pa /
NK101(de)005:21: chos gang yang ma yin pa'i rang bzhin lhan cig
NK101(de)005:22: skyes pa des ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK101(de)005:23: skyed par byed pas na kun gzhi bya ba yin
NK101(de)005:25: kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin te //
NK101(de)005:26: mya ngan 'das pa'i gzhi ma'ang yin //
NK101(de)005:28: de nyid sangs rgyas rnams kyis rang ngo rig pas rig thog der grol bas grol gzhi yin la /
NK101(de)005:29: sems can rnams kyi rang ngo ma shes par gzhan
NK101(de)005:30: du gzung bas bzung 'dzin gyis 'phrul snang 'di dag
NK101(de)005:31: shar bas 'khrul gzhi yang yin te kun tu bzang
NK101(de)005:32: po'i dgongs pa zangs thal du bstan pa'i rgyud las
NK101(de)005:33: / kun gyi gzhi ni 'dus ma byas //
NK101(de)005:34: rang byung klong yang brjod du med //
NK101(de)005:36: de nyid rig na sangs rgyas te //
NK101(de)005:39: de lta bu'i sems kun gyi gzhi de nyid ma
NK101(de)005:40: rig pa rig par bya ba'i thabs lam lta bsgom
NK101(de)005:42: lta ba'i ngo bo ni sems rang bzhin gyis spros pa dang bral ba de nyid yin te /
NK101(de)005:43: de yang stong pa nyid kyis rang bzhin du ye nas lhun gyis grub pas skye ba med pa /
NK101(de)005:44: skye ba med pa nam mkha' lta bu'i stong pa
NK101(de)005:45: de'i gdangs las 'khor 'das kyis chos thams cad sprin
NK101(de)005:46: dang na bun ltar gzhi la med bzhin du snang
NK101(de)005:47: bar nus pas 'gag pa med pa /
NK101(de)005:48: de ltar gnang yang stong pa nyid las ma 'das pas gnas pa med pa /
NK101(de)005:49: dbyibs dang kha dog dang dngos po dang mtshan ma thams cad du ma grub pa /
NK101(de)005:50: 'di nyid do zhes ngos bzung du med pa /
NK101(de)005:51: dper na bar snang gi ser bu ltar yod pa'i
NK101(de)005:52: dngos por ma grub kyang med pa ma yin te
NK101(de)005:55: gang du yang song ba med pa'i bun ne ba 'di lta bu ste /
NK101(de)005:60: rnam par shes pa'i phung po thams cad las 'das pa /
NK101(de)005:63: phyi bzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems med pa /
NK101(de)005:64: bdag gzhan dang srog dang byed pa po la sogs pa rtog pa thams cad med pa /
NK101(de)005:65: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyis bar la sogs pa chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin /
NK101(de)005:66: gang du yang ma grub pas ngo bo med pa /
NK101(de)005:67: gar yang snang bas ngos bzung med pa /
NK101(de)005:68: de lta bur ye gdod ma nas gnas pas med pa ma yin /
NK101(de)005:69: dngos po dang mtshan mar ma grub pas yod pa ma yin /
NK101(de)005:70: yod med gnyis su ma grub pas gnyis ka la yin pa'ang ma yin te /
NK101(de)005:71: bad sa la'i rgyal po 'char byed la gdams pa'i
NK101(de)005:72: mdo las 'khor ba med pas mya ngan 'das pa'ang
NK101(de)005:73: med / yod pa ma grub pas na med pa'ang med /
NK101(de)005:74: gnyis ga min pas gnyis ga min pa'ang min /
NK101(de)005:77: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK101(de)005:78: gzungs dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK101(de)005:79: chos bdag med par mnyam pa nyid //
NK101(de)005:80: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pas //
NK101(de)005:81: stong pa nyid kyis rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)005:83: dbu ma rin chen 'phreng ba las //
NK101(de)005:84: skye ba rgyu dang bcas mthong na //
NK101(de)005:85: ci yi phyir na med par brjod //
NK101(de)005:86: rgyu dang bcas pa'ang 'gag mthong na //
NK101(de)005:87: ci yi phyir na yod par brjod //
NK101(de)005:90: yod dang med pa 'di dag mtha' yin la //
NK101(de)005:91: gtsang dang mi gtsang 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK101(de)005:92: de ltar mtha' bzhi rnam par spangs pa yis //
NK101(de)005:93: mkhas pa dbus la'ang gnas par mi bya'o //
NK101(de)005:96: phyi rol dngos po yod med min //
NK101(de)005:97: sems kyang yongs su bzung ba med //
NK101(de)005:98: lta ba thams cad rab spangs pa //
NK101(de)005:99: de ni skye med mtshan nyid do //
NK101(de)005:103: 'phags pa rab 'byor ci chos ma skyes pa rnams skyes ba'am /
NK101(de)005:106: tshe dang ldan pa sha ri'i bu kho bo ni ma skyes pa yang skye bar mi 'dod /
NK101(de)005:107: skyes pa yang skye bar mi 'dod do //
NK101(de)005:109: deng sang dge ba'i bshes bsnyen 'ga' zhig lta ba'i
NK101(de)005:110: gnas lugs ci yang med pa la bzhed pa ni
NK101(de)005:111: 'phags pa klu bsgrub kyis bkag ste /
NK101(de)005:114: med nyid bsgrub pa ma yin no //
NK101(de)005:116: dbu ma rtsa ba shes rab las /
NK101(de)005:117: yod ces bya bar rtag par 'dzin //
NK101(de)005:118: med ces bya bar chad par blta //
NK101(de)005:119: de phyir yod dang med pa la //
NK101(de)005:120: mkhas pas gnas par mi bya'o //
NK101(de)005:122: de la cang med du 'dod pa ni mu stegs
NK101(de)005:123: rgyang 'phen pa'i chad blta dang mtshungs pas ngan 'gror
NK101(de)005:129: gang la stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK101(de)005:130: de dag gsor mi rung par gsungs //
NK101(de)005:132: 'phags pa dkon mchog rtsegs pa las /
NK101(de)005:133: 'od bsrungs gang zag tu blta ba ri rab tsam ni bla'i /
NK101(de)005:134: mngon pa'i nga rgyal can stong pa nyid du lta ba ni de lta ma yin no //
NK101(de)005:136: 'o na ci med par gsungs pa rnams kyi dgongs don gang zhe na /
NK101(de)005:137: de ni gang zag bdag tu lta ba rnams kyis
NK101(de)005:138: dngos por 'dzin pa bzlog pa'i slad du gsungs pa
NK101(de)005:139: yin la / ri bong gis rwa ltar cang med du 'dod pa ma yin te /
NK101(de)005:141: gal te stong pa thabs yin na //
NK101(de)005:142: de tshe sangs rgyas nyid mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)005:143: rgyu las 'bras bu gzhan med phyir //
NK101(de)005:144: thabs ni stong pa nyid ma yin //
NK101(de)005:145: lta ba rnams las log rnams dang //
NK101(de)005:146: bdag tu blta ba tshol rnams kyis //
NK101(de)005:147: bdag tu 'dzin pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)005:148: rgyal ba rnams kyis stong par bstan //
NK101(de)005:151: thub pas stong nyid sngags pa ni /
NK101(de)005:152: dngos por 'dzin pa bzlog phyir yin //
NK101(de)005:153: seng ge gangs la mi skrags te //
NK101(de)005:154: me cher mthong na skrag ces bya //
NK101(de)005:155: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa' yang //
NK101(de)005:156: chos gzhan dag la mi skrag ste //
NK101(de)005:157: stong pa nyid la skrag ces gsungs //
NK101(de)005:159: de ltar stong pa nyid khang stong mis stong pa lta bu nyi tshe ba'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK101(de)005:160: ci yang med pa chad lta'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK101(de)005:161: dngos med tsam gyis stong pa nyid dang /
NK101(de)005:162: bem po'i stong pa nyid dang /
NK101(de)005:163: rgyas 'debs kyis stong pa nyid la sogs pa'i yang dag pa'i lam ma yin te /
NK101(de)005:165: phung po rnam dpyad stong pa rnams //
NK101(de)005:166: chu shing ji bzhin snying po med //
NK101(de)005:167: rnam pa thams cad mchog ldan pa'i //
NK101(de)005:168: stong nyid de ltar 'gyur ma yin //
NK101(de)005:169: skye ba med pa 'gag med pa'i //
NK101(de)005:170: shes bya gang zhig 'dir mthong ba //
NK101(de)005:171: stong pa'i dngos po stong pa nyid //
NK101(de)005:172: phung po rnams rnam dpyad pa min //
NK101(de)005:174: 'phags pa brgyad stong pa las kyang sha ri'i bus smras pa /
NK101(de)005:175: 'phags pa rab 'byor ci sems med pa nyid de gang yin /
NK101(de)005:177: tshe dang ldan pa sha ri'i bu /
NK101(de)005:178: sems med pa de ni 'gyur ba med pa rnam par rtog pa med pa'o //
NK101(de)005:181: rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub /
NK101(de)005:182: ces sogs kyis gsal ba yin no //
NK101(de)005:183: yang kha gcig rgyal sras 'brom gyis /
NK101(de)005:184: kho bo'i dbu ma'i lta ba ci yang ma yin
NK101(de)005:185: pa bya ba yin zhes gsungs pa de med dgag
NK101(de)005:186: yin te / tshad ma rnam nges su chos kyis grags pas /
NK101(de)005:187: med par dgag pa ni ci yang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)005:188: zhes bshad pa yin no gsungs pa dag 'dod de /
NK101(de)005:189: yang dag pa'i don rtog ge'i yul las 'das pa de'i don cung zad ma dgongs pa 'dra'o //
NK101(de)005:190: mdor na sems yod med yin min gang du yang ma grub pas /
NK101(de)005:191: ngos bzungs dang khas len dang dam bca' ba med
NK101(de)005:192: pa gang du yang mi 'dzin pa de 'di'i blta
NK101(de)005:193: ba yin te / dri med 'od las /
NK101(de)005:194: yod med med min yod med min /
NK101(de)005:195: gnyis kha'i bdag nyid min pa'ang min /
NK101(de)005:196: mtha' bzhi las ni rnam grol ba /
NK101(de)005:197: de nyid dbu ma pa yis rigs /
NK101(de)005:200: gal te dngos gang dam bca' yod /
NK101(de)005:201: de na nga la skyon de yod /
NK101(de)005:202: nga la dam bca' med pas na /
NK101(de)005:203: nga ni skyon med kho na yin /
NK101(de)005:206: khas mi len pa'i blta ba dang /
NK101(de)005:208: zhes bshad pas mi 'thad do snyam na /
NK101(de)005:209: 'dir gang du yang khas len rgyu med pas te /
NK101(de)005:210: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)005:211: don dam blo yis spyod yul min //
NK101(de)005:212: blo 'di kun rdzob yin phyir ro //
NK101(de)005:214: de ni theg pa gsum po rang rang gi sgor
NK101(de)005:215: bzhugs nas de dang de'i lta ba khas mi len
NK101(de)005:218: chos nyid spyi'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa de nyid /
NK101(de)005:219: sems can shes rab chung pas med par go /
NK101(de)005:222: gang tshe dngos dang dngos med dag /
NK101(de)005:223: blo yis mdun na mi gnas pas //
NK101(de)005:224: de tshe rnam pa gzhan med pas //
NK101(de)005:225: dmigs pa med par rab tu zhi //
NK101(de)005:227: de dag gis ni theg pa chen po'i mdo brgyud
NK101(de)005:228: man ngag rnams kyi lta ba'i dgongs don phyin ci
NK101(de)005:229: ma log par bstan pa yin no //
NK101(de)005:230: spyi don gnyis pa bsgom pa'i tshul bshad pa ni /
NK101(de)005:231: gong du ba stan pa'i lta ba'i gnas lugs de
NK101(de)005:232: nyid rtogs nas mngon du 'gyur bar bya ba'i thabs
NK101(de)005:233: yin te / jo bo chen po rjes /
NK101(de)005:234: stong nyid rtog pas grol 'gyur gyis /
NK101(de)005:235: bsgom pa lhag ma de don yin /
NK101(de)005:237: de la gang zag dbang po 'bring man chad kyis thogs mar zhi gnas la bslab ste /
NK101(de)005:239: rnam rtog ma rig chen po ste //
NK101(de)005:240: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung byed yin //
NK101(de)005:241: mi rtog ting 'dzin la gnas na //
NK101(de)005:242: nam mkha' bzhin du rtog med gsal //
NK101(de)005:245: tha mal rnam rtog ma rtogs pa /
NK101(de)005:246: srid dag sdug bsngal gzhan med pa /
NK101(de)005:250: mig mi 'dzum par lta dang mi bsal dang //
NK101(de)005:251: rlung 'gog pa ni bla ma dam pa'i lung //
NK101(de)005:254: zhi gnas rab tu ldan pa'i lhag mthong gis //
NK101(de)005:255: nyon mongs rnam par spongs ba shes byas nas //
NK101(de)005:256: thog mar zhi gnas rtsal bya de yang ni //
NK101(de)005:257: 'jig rten chags pa med la mngon dgas gzhol //
NK101(de)005:259: lus rnam snang gi chos bdun dang ldan pas /
NK101(de)005:260: ngas ji srid mnyam par bzhag rin la rnam par rtog pa zhi ba cig bya'o snyam du dam bca'/
NK101(de)005:261: rnam rtog gang shar gyis rjes su ma 'brang par
NK101(de)005:262: sems blod nas ma yengs par bzhag pas re zhig
NK101(de)005:263: nas zhi gnas kyis nyams skye bo /
NK101(de)005:265: dang po rtog pa bkag nas bsgom /
NK101(de)005:267: de nas lhag mthong la bslabs par bya ste /
NK101(de)005:268: de la lhag mthong zhes bya ba ni rtogs pa
NK101(de)005:269: mi dgegs par gang shar ba de ngo shes tsam
NK101(de)005:270: gyi ngang la 'jog pa yin la /
NK101(de)005:271: 'di las lhag pa'i bsgom zhig logs su med do //
NK101(de)005:272: de la mdo dgongs pa nges 'grel las /
NK101(de)005:274: bcom ldan 'das du zhig gi zhi gnas kyis dmigs pa lags /
NK101(de)005:276: gcig ste rnam par mi rtog pa'i gzugs brnyan no //
NK101(de)005:278: bcom ldan 'das du zhig gis lhag mthong gi dmigs pa lags /
NK101(de)005:280: gcig ste rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pa'i gzugs brnyan no //
NK101(de)005:282: 'di ltar rnam par rtog pa gang shar ba de
NK101(de)005:283: rang la che re bltas pas rang grol du stong
NK101(de)005:285: blta nas blta brgyu med kyis de ngo shes tsam
NK101(de)005:286: byas nas 'jog pa yin des dpe rkun ma ngo
NK101(de)005:287: shes na ma skrad par rang log 'gro ba ltar
NK101(de)005:288: ro // yang stong phyam pa dang /
NK101(de)005:291: rtog med la sogs pa yong du re ba'ang mi bya ste gang byung gis thog tu bzhag /
NK101(de)005:292: byung na'ang de kha ngo shes tsam du slod nas 'jog pa yin gyis /
NK101(de)005:293: bsgom du ci yang med la /
NK101(de)005:294: bsgom du med pa'i ngang la ma yengs tsam du 'jog pa 'di la dran pa'am /
NK101(de)005:295: shes bzhin zhes bya ste rgyun du ma bral bar bya'o //
NK101(de)005:296: de ltar yang slob dpon sh+ri sing has /
NK101(de)005:297: bsgom ma myong dang 'bral ma myong /
NK101(de)005:298: mi bsgom don dang mi 'bral ba /
NK101(de)005:300: de ltar rnam rtog gang shar la bzo bcos ma byas par bzhag pas na rang thog tu grol /
NK101(de)005:302: de gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa ni shar grol dus mnyam shes bya ste /
NK101(de)005:303: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK101(de)005:304: yin pa grub pa med pa'i rig pa 'di //
NK101(de)005:305: rang snang 'char tshul cir yang ma 'gag pas //
NK101(de)005:306: snang srid kun kyang chos sku'i zhing du shar //
NK101(de)005:307: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK101(de)005:309: mkhas grub blo gros rabs yangs gyis //
NK101(de)005:310: sems la sems kyis tshur ltas pas //
NK101(de)005:311: skye 'gag gnas gsum spros dang bral //
NK101(de)005:312: kha dog dbyibs 'das mtshan mas stong //
NK101(de)005:313: ngos gzungs kun dang bral ba yis //
NK101(de)005:314: stong pa nyid du thag chod la //
NK101(de)005:315: 'dzin med ngang la yengs med zhog /
NK101(de)005:316: bzhag tshe gnas na gnas mkhan bltos //
NK101(de)005:318: bltas tshe ngos bzung med pas na //
NK101(de)005:319: gnas 'gyu thams cad stong par gcig /
NK101(de)005:322: de la shar grol dus mnyam zer //
NK101(de)005:323: de la rang shar rang grol zer //
NK101(de)005:324: de la ye dag ye grol zer //
NK101(de)005:325: de la chos sku'i yo lang zer //
NK101(de)005:326: de la yeng med rgyun du zhog /
NK101(de)005:328: 'o na tshogs drug gi yul du snang ba 'di dag lam du ji ltar mkhyer zhes na /
NK101(de)005:329: mig gi yul du gzugs su snang ba phyi rol
NK101(de)005:330: gyi sa brdo ri brag rtsi shing nags tshal khang
NK101(de)005:332: mi dang dud 'gro la sogs pa nang bcud kyis sems can dang /
NK101(de)005:333: dkar dmar mthing ga la sogs pa'i kha dog dang /
NK101(de)005:334: dgra dang gnyen la sogs pa mdor na mig gi gang mthong ba'i rtog pa /
NK101(de)005:336: gzugs dang sgra dang de bzhin dri //
NK101(de)005:337: ro dang reg bya skyes pa'i dngos //
NK101(de)005:338: rin chen sems 'di brjod nyid de //
NK101(de)005:339: chos dbyings mchog tu zhi ba'o //
NK101(de)005:340: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dngos //
NK101(de)005:341: 'du byed dang ni rnam shes nyid //
NK101(de)005:342: thams cad sems 'di'i ngo bo las //
NK101(de)005:343: thub pas gzhan du ma gsungs so //
NK101(de)005:344: yid bzhin nor bu chen po ni //
NK101(de)005:346: dben zhing dga' ba'i sems nyid kyis //
NK101(de)005:347: sangs rgyas byang chub 'bras rab ster //
NK101(de)005:355: snyam pa la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pa gang
NK101(de)005:356: shar ba de rang gi thog tu lhod de bslod
NK101(de)005:358: rgyal po 'char byed kyis mdo las /
NK101(de)005:359: dngos 'di spangs nas stong nyid mi rtsam gyis /
NK101(de)005:360: snang pa nyid na stong pa nyid yin phyir /
NK101(de)005:363: 'di ltar mig gi yul du snang ba yis /
NK101(de)005:364: phyi nang snod bcud dngos po thams cad kun //
NK101(de)005:365: snang yang bden 'dzin med pa'i ngang la zhog /
NK101(de)005:367: gzugs snang stong dbyer med du grol ba'o //
NK101(de)005:368: de bzhin sna ba'i yul du chu sgra dang rlung la sogs pa 'byung pa'i sgra dang /
NK101(de)005:373: snyan pa dang mi snyan pa la sogs pa'i gtam
NK101(de)005:374: sogs gang thos pa de nyid la bzo med du
NK101(de)005:375: bzhag pas sgra grags stong du grol ba ste /
NK101(de)005:377: 'di ltar snang ba'i yul du grags pa yis //
NK101(de)005:378: snyan dang mi snyan 'dzin pa'i sgra rnams kun //
NK101(de)005:379: grags stong bsam sno bral ba'i ngang la zhog /
NK101(de)005:381: de bzhin du sna'i yul du spos la sogs pa'i zhim pa'i dri dang /
NK101(de)005:382: gshang lci la sogs pa smre ba'i dri sogs gang
NK101(de)005:383: tshor yang 'dzin med du de kha'i thog tu bzhag
NK101(de)005:384: pas dri tshor stong du grol ba'o //
NK101(de)005:385: lce'i yul du kha zas ro drug gi rnam pa
NK101(de)005:386: gang myangs yang de la 'dzin med du ngang la
NK101(de)005:387: bzhag pas ro myong stong du grol ba'o //
NK101(de)005:388: lus kyis yul du dar zab la sogs pa reg bya 'jam pa dang /
NK101(de)005:389: re ba dang tsher ma la sogs pa rtsub pa dang /
NK101(de)005:390: grang ba dang dro ba la sogs pa gang byung kyang /
NK101(de)005:391: de ka la gzo med du bzhag pas reg stong du grol ba'o //
NK101(de)005:392: yid kyis yul du bskyid sdug legs nyes bya ba
NK101(de)005:393: che chung gi rtog pa gang shar ba de ka'i
NK101(de)005:394: ngo bo la bcos bslad med par bzhag pas rnam
NK101(de)005:395: par rtog pa rang grol ba ste /
NK101(de)005:397: 'di ltar yid kyis yul du 'gyu ba yis /
NK101(de)005:398: nyon mongs dug lnga'i rtog pa ci shar yang /
NK101(de)005:399: sngon bsu rjes spyod blo yis bcos mi bzhugs /
NK101(de)005:400: 'gyu ba rang sar dag pas chos skur grol /
NK101(de)005:402: dam pa po dang bsgom smon gyis lo rgyus lta bu'o //
NK101(de)005:403: de ltar gang shar gyi thog tu gzo bcos mi
NK101(de)005:404: bya bar rang gi ngo bo la ltas nas 'jog
NK101(de)005:405: pa yin gyis / rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK101(de)005:406: dbang po rnams ni yul rnams la //
NK101(de)005:407: 'jug cing rtag tu gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)005:408: bdag med chos la yang dag gnas //
NK101(de)005:409: 'di ni dam tshig mchog yin no //
NK101(de)005:412: gzugs rnams sna tshogs lta ba dang /
NK101(de)005:413: sgra ni rgyas par nyan pa dang /
NK101(de)005:414: sna tshogs ro ni za ba dang /
NK101(de)005:415: smra ba dang ni rgod pa dang //
NK101(de)005:416: las de rnams ni byed pa na //
NK101(de)005:417: de nyid rig pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK101(de)005:420: 'di ni dbang po rgya yan gyis //
NK101(de)005:421: gdam ngag bya ba dper na skyes bu tha mal ba dang 'dra ste /
NK101(de)005:422: lam pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang gnyis ngo shes ma shes kyi khyad las med pas /
NK101(de)005:424: dbang po rgya yan gyi gdams ngag dang sgo gsum tha mal du shor ba gnyis /
NK101(de)005:427: bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i mdo las /
NK101(de)005:429: dge slong rnal 'byor spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams ji lta bu lags /
NK101(de)005:432: dper na thab kyi me bsad na dkar khung gi du ba chad pa ltar /
NK101(de)005:433: sems stong par shes bzhin rig pas gzugs snang stong
NK101(de)005:434: sgra grags stong dri tshor stong ro myong stong reg
NK101(de)005:435: bya reg stong gis nyams 'byung ste /
NK101(de)005:436: nam mkha' ma sgribs na gsal /
NK101(de)005:437: chu ma myogs na dngas so /
NK101(de)005:439: sems ngo shes pa'i dge slong gang /
NK101(de)005:440: ji ltar spyad kyang bsgom pa'i ngang /
NK101(de)005:441: snyug ma'i don la gnas pa yin //
NK101(de)005:444: sgo lnga'i rnam shes gsal ba la //
NK101(de)005:445: yid kyis zhen rtogs ma zhugs na //
NK101(de)005:446: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa de ka dang //
NK101(de)005:448: de ltar rnam par rtog pa gang shar rang babs
NK101(de)005:449: su bzhag pa de rnam rtog ltar snang mod kyang
NK101(de)005:451: rtog pa'i gnad tshang rig pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis /
NK101(de)005:452: rnam rtog ltar snang des 'ching nus pa ma yin te /
NK101(de)005:453: gung thang pa lha dbang blo gros /
NK101(de)005:454: ji ltar thag pa mes tshig thal ba de //
NK101(de)005:455: thag pa'i gzugs su gnang yang 'ching mi nus //
NK101(de)005:456: de bzhin gzhi rtsa spyad pa'i sems nyid 'di //
NK101(de)005:457: nyon mongs dug lngar shar yang 'ching mi nus //
NK101(de)005:459: de bas na ma rig pa'i skye bo rnams ni rnam par rtog pas 'ching mod kyis /
NK101(de)005:460: rnam rtog gis rang bzhin rig pa dag ni rnam rtog des kas grol bas na /
NK101(de)005:461: bde mchog nyung ngu'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)005:463: des ni mkhas pa yongs su grol //
NK101(de)005:466: rba brlabs de ka chu yin pa ltar sems las sna tshogs su shar yang /
NK101(de)005:467: shar ba de ka sems yin pas de'i rang bzhin shes pa de kho nas chog ste /
NK101(de)005:469: ngo bo stong ste yul du bzung bas 'khrul //
NK101(de)005:470: byed mkhan mtshan nyid bltos gcig ding ri ba //
NK101(de)005:472: rje btsun mi ta dzo gis /
NK101(de)005:473: rnam rtog stong pa min na rtog med sgom dgos pa la /
NK101(de)005:474: rnam rtog kho rang stong par 'dug pas rtog med gud nas rtsal mi dgos /
NK101(de)005:475: thag nye ba bzhag nas ring ba bskor nas ci bya /
NK101(de)005:477: snang mkhan ngos zin na snang pa skyon min te /
NK101(de)005:478: slar snang pa de nyid ye shes kyis rol par
NK101(de)005:479: 'char bas snang ba la stong pas rgyas thebs pa
NK101(de)005:481: rnam rtog dang snang ba sems gsum dbyer med pa'i stong pa yin pa la /
NK101(de)005:482: yin thog de rang du bzhag pas chog pa nyams len shin tu bsla ba lags /
NK101(de)005:483: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyis sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK101(de)005:484: gang skyes snyug ma nyid yin phyir //
NK101(de)005:485: gang shar dran pas ma brjed na //
NK101(de)005:486: de shar stong pa nyid du dag /
NK101(de)005:487: rnal 'byor dbang phyug nyid du dag /
NK101(de)005:489: bu nyon khyod gang rnam par rtog /'dis bdag ma bcing ma grol phyir //
NK101(de)005:490: ma yengs ma bcos rang gar ni //
NK101(de)005:491: kye ho dub pa ngal gsos shig /
NK101(de)005:493: 'dir kha gcig phyi gzung ba'i yul dang /
NK101(de)005:494: nang 'dzin pa'i sems thams cad stong pa nyid du
NK101(de)005:495: blos bcos nas bsgom pa'i lugs yod par grags la
NK101(de)005:496: / de jo bo'i lugs yin zer /
NK101(de)005:497: jo bo'i gsung rabs rnams su ni de ltar mi snang la /
NK101(de)005:498: jo bos gser gling rgyal po bla ma skyongs la gnang ba'i man ngag las /
NK101(de)005:499: ji srid du mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa'i dgra
NK101(de)005:500: ma langs kyis bar du de lta bu la shes
NK101(de)005:502: zhes gsungs pa ni zhi gnas kyi skabs yin la /
NK101(de)005:505: bar skabs der ci la yang mi rtog /
NK101(de)005:506: cir yang mi 'dzin zhes sogs gsungs pas /
NK101(de)005:507: lugs de lta bur stong par bsgom pa ma gsungs zhing /
NK101(de)005:508: med par bsgom pa ni bcos ma rnam rtog rang rgyud pa yin te /
NK101(de)005:510: thogs ma med nas da lta'i bar //
NK101(de)005:512: gshis las 'khrul nas bcos pas lan //
NK101(de)005:514: sems kyi rang bzhin nam gnas lugs 'gag med du gnas pa yin pas /
NK101(de)005:515: rnam par rtog pa dkag pas mii khegs te gar yang 'char /
NK101(de)005:516: 'gog pa la snyoms par zhugs pa dag dang /
NK101(de)005:517: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i lha la sogs pa dag kyang
NK101(de)005:518: ting nge 'dzin de las sad pa na slar 'khor
NK101(de)005:519: bar ltung / rje dwags po rin po ches kyang /
NK101(de)005:520: bsgom chen pa ni rnam rtog med pa gcig 'dod //
NK101(de)005:521: rnam rtog ni bkag pas mi khegs //
NK101(de)005:524: rnam rtog bkag pas stong pa bsgom pa 'di ni rdo rje 'chang gis bkag ste //
NK101(de)005:526: stong pa sgom par mi bya zhing //
NK101(de)005:527: stong min bsgom par mi bya'o //
NK101(de)005:528: stong dang stong min gzung ba las //
NK101(de)005:529: rtog pa nyung min skye bar 'gyur //
NK101(de)005:530: yongs su spang na kun rtog ste //
NK101(de)005:531: de phyir de ni yang dag spangs //
NK101(de)005:533: phyi rol gyi dngos po dang /
NK101(de)005:534: nang gi 'dzin pa gang yin pa dag kyang gdod
NK101(de)005:535: ma nas stong zhing bdag med pa yin pa la
NK101(de)005:536: stong pa'o snyam du bsgom mi dgos te /
NK101(de)005:537: rang gis rang la nga yin snyam du bsgom mi dgos pa bzhin no //
NK101(de)005:538: de bas na phyi nang gi chos thams cad ye
NK101(de)005:539: nas sems kyi rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gnas
NK101(de)005:540: pa de la so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK101(de)005:541: rigs rtsal las gzhan pa'i spangs blangs gang yang med
NK101(de)005:542: de / 'phags pa dkon mchog rtsegs pa las /
NK101(de)005:543: 'od bsrung byang chub sems dpa' tshul bzhin du chos la sbyor ba gang zhe na /
NK101(de)005:544: dbu ma'i lam chos rnams la so sor yang dag par rtogs zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)005:546: des ni rtogs med kyi don mthong ba med pa'i tshul gyi mthong bar 'gyur te /
NK101(de)005:548: rtog med tshul gyis mthong bas na /
NK101(de)005:549: stong nyid mthong zhes tha snyad btags /
NK101(de)005:550: ma mthong ba nyid de mthong bar /
NK101(de)005:551: shin tu zab pa'i mdo las gsungs /
NK101(de)005:553: de ltar bsgom du med pa'i ngang la ma bcos
NK101(de)005:554: par rang babs su bzhag pa 'di kho na las
NK101(de)005:559: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zab mo
NK101(de)005:560: 'di ni su'i kyang bsgom kyang bsgom par bgyi ba
NK101(de)005:561: ma lags / su yang mi bsgom /
NK101(de)005:563: gang la yang bsgom par bgyi ba ma mchis so //
NK101(de)005:564: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
NK101(de)005:565: bcom ldan 'das shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK101(de)005:566: pa la chos gang yang yongs su grub pa ma
NK101(de)005:569: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom pa 'di ni nam mkha' bsgom pa'o //
NK101(de)005:570: 'di lta ste shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK101(de)005:571: pa bsgom pa 'di ni chos thams cad mi bsgom
NK101(de)005:572: pa lags so // 'di lta ste shes rab kyi
NK101(de)005:573: pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom pa 'di ni ma
NK101(de)005:574: chags pa bsgom pa lags so //
NK101(de)005:577: bsgom med bsgom pa po yang med //
NK101(de)005:578: gang yang rnam par bsgom pa'ang med //
NK101(de)005:579: bsgom bya nyid kyang yod min pa //
NK101(de)005:580: de yi de nyid bsgom par brjod //
NK101(de)005:583: gang du yid kyi ma bsgom na //
NK101(de)005:585: bsgom pa med pa'i bsgom nyid kyis //
NK101(de)005:586: chos rnams thams cad yongs shes bya //
NK101(de)005:588: 'o na dran pa rten pa de ka bsgoms yin no ce na /
NK101(de)005:589: dran pa zhes pa gang shar la ma bcos par bzhag pa yin la /
NK101(de)005:590: de la bsgom mi bsgom gnyis ka'i tha snyad med do //
NK101(de)005:591: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston gyis kyang /
NK101(de)005:592: mi rtag stong pa sogs su zhen na'ang mtshan 'dzin
NK101(de)005:593: gzhi shes bya ste byang sems kyi spangs byar gsungs
NK101(de)005:595: gang du yang 'dzin pa med par bzhag pa ni gnad kyi dam pa'o //
NK101(de)005:597: sangs rgyas kyis dgongs pa ni sems can gyis blo'i
NK101(de)005:598: yul las 'das pas da lta so so skye bos
NK101(de)005:599: bsgom par mi nus so zhes zer /
NK101(de)005:600: de ltar na ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa thams cad don med du 'gyur zhing /
NK101(de)005:601: g.yag sde pan chen gyis kyang /
NK101(de)005:602: don dam blo'i spyod yul min ces pa /
NK101(de)005:603: rtog pa la blor bzhed pa yin /
NK101(de)005:604: rig tsam la blor byas na don dam de'i spyod
NK101(de)005:605: yul ma yin par byas na chos nyid rtog bya
NK101(de)005:607: rtog mi srid pa'i skyon yod /
NK101(de)005:609: bde gshegs 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las kyang /
NK101(de)005:610: yang dag bden pa de bzhin nyid /
NK101(de)005:611: ma nor ma bcos ma rtsal ba /
NK101(de)005:612: ma skyes ma 'gag mi dmigs pa /
NK101(de)005:613: snying po byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK101(de)005:614: 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos shing //
NK101(de)005:615: yon tan gyis kyang ma reg pa //
NK101(de)005:616: rnal ma rang byung mtshan nyid bral //
NK101(de)005:617: brjod med bsam 'das chos kyis sku //
NK101(de)005:618: byang chub chen po de nyid de //
NK101(de)005:619: bsgrub tu med de mthong du med //
NK101(de)005:620: rtsal du med de rtog tu yod //
NK101(de)005:621: grub tu med de snang du yod //
NK101(de)005:622: gnas lugs don gyis rta mgrin yin //
NK101(de)005:624: lung gi yid ches bskyed pa'i rim pa gzhan yang /
NK101(de)005:625: mtshan mo bzang po'i mdo las /
NK101(de)005:627: ma 'ongs pa la re ba med //
NK101(de)005:628: da ltar byung chos gang yin pa //
NK101(de)005:629: de dang de la rnam lta ba //
NK101(de)005:631: de ltar mkhas pas spel bar bya //
NK101(de)005:634: de ltar skyes pa'i rgyun rnams ni //
NK101(de)005:635: mkhas pas yongs su bskyangs par byed //
NK101(de)005:637: de nyid rab tu mi gnas pas /
NK101(de)005:639: ngo mtshar rdo rje sangs rgyas mchog /
NK101(de)005:640: sems ni skye med de shes nas //
NK101(de)005:641: bsgom par bya ba ma yin te //
NK101(de)005:642: rang gar bzhag na bde ba che //
NK101(de)005:645: tha mal shes pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mchog /
NK101(de)005:646: ma bcos bzhag na sku gsum 'bras bu thob //
NK101(de)005:647: rang gar bslod na mthar phyin ye shes yin //
NK101(de)005:648: sems nyid ma bcos rdo rje kun gyi ngang //
NK101(de)005:649: rnam mar bzhag pa'i don de mtshon du med //
NK101(de)005:650: 'di ni dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyis yum //
NK101(de)005:653: ma bcos ma bcos blo ma bcos //
NK101(de)005:654: blo yi bcos pa'i chos rnams ni //
NK101(de)005:655: ri bas lci zhing mtsho bas zab //
NK101(de)005:658: ma bcos par bzhag pa rang gi 'ong ste //
NK101(de)005:659: thog ma med pa nas da lta'i bar du 'khrul
NK101(de)005:660: pa 'di ma bcos par 'jog ma shes pa rang
NK101(de)005:662: de ltar gang bsgom du med kyang yengs su med
NK101(de)005:663: pa'i nyams len brtson par ma byas na go yul
NK101(de)005:664: dang kha lta la song nas mi phan te /
NK101(de)005:666: gang la'ang skyon du mi lta zhing //
NK101(de)005:667: ci yang ma yin nyams su blang //
NK101(de)005:668: drod rtags la sogs 'dod mi bya //
NK101(de)005:669: bsgom du med par bstan mod kyang //
NK101(de)005:670: le lo btang snyoms dbang mi btang //
NK101(de)005:671: rgyun du dran pas bsgom par bya //
NK101(de)005:674: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen
NK101(de)005:675: po bgyi ba gang gis slad du shes rab kyi
NK101(de)005:676: pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom par bgyi ba de
NK101(de)005:677: yang bgyi la / shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa de yang rtog pa ma mchis so //
NK101(de)005:678: de ci'i slad du shes na shes rab kyi /
NK101(de)005:679: pha rol tu phyin pa la rnam par rtog pa ma mchis pa'i slad du'o //
NK101(de)005:681: sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK101(de)005:682: ji ltar 'gro ba mang po la /
NK101(de)005:683: zas dang bskom dag byin byas kyang /
NK101(de)005:684: rang nyid bskres pas shi ba ltar //
NK101(de)005:685: chos la ma bsgom de dang 'dra //
NK101(de)005:688: ji ltar yongs su ma bsgom par /
NK101(de)005:689: chos nyid mthong par mi 'gyur te //
NK101(de)005:690: chu ni mthong dang thos pa yis //
NK101(de)005:691: ma mthung bskom pa ji ltar sel //
NK101(de)005:693: gsang ba bdud rtsi'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)005:694: bsgom rgyu brdul tsam med pa la //
NK101(de)005:695: yengs rgyu skad gcig med pa 'di //
NK101(de)005:696: lha yi rgyal po yin par 'dod //
NK101(de)005:697: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog gyur pa //
NK101(de)005:698: rang rig ye shes me bo che //
NK101(de)005:699: thams cad 'di la gnas pa ste //
NK101(de)005:700: mchod dang gtor ma la sogs pa //
NK101(de)005:701: las dang bya ba sna tshogs kun //
NK101(de)005:702: sems kyi de nyid shes gyur na //
NK101(de)005:703: thams cad 'di la gnas par shes //
NK101(de)005:705: de ltar rnam rtog gzo med du bzhag pas rtog pa thams cad rang grol /
NK101(de)005:706: dang gsal spros pa med pa ye shes brten par 'char te /
NK101(de)005:707: de ngang las gnas pa ni mnyam bzhag zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)005:708: thun mtshams dang 'gro 'chag nyal 'dug thams cad dran pas skyong ba la rjes thob zhes zer /
NK101(de)005:709: mnyam rjes 'bres nas rmi lam du yang bsgom dang
NK101(de)005:710: mi 'bral ba ni 'od gsal 'khor yug gam rdo
NK101(de)005:711: rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin ces bya ste /
NK101(de)005:712: de tsa na spyan dang mngon par shes pa la
NK101(de)005:713: sogs pa'i yon tan kyang rang shugs la 'ong la
NK101(de)005:714: / rnal 'byor bzhi'i nyams yang rim gyis 'char ro //
NK101(de)005:715: rnal 'byor bzhi po 'di kha gcig nyams yin par bzhed /
NK101(de)005:716: kha gcig rtog par bzhed cing /
NK101(de)005:717: rnal 'byor bzhi sum cu gnyis su phye ba dang /
NK101(de)005:718: rje rang byung rdo rjes ni /
NK101(de)005:720: rtog pa'i rnal 'byor bzhir phye la 'dir ni ro gcig man chad nyams dang /
NK101(de)005:721: bsgom med ni rtog par 'dod do //
NK101(de)005:722: de yang nyams 'gyur ba can yin pas ro gcig bsgom med du 'gyur dgos la /
NK101(de)005:723: rtog pa ni mi 'gyur ba yin pas /
NK101(de)005:724: bsgom med nas 'gyur ba med pas so //
NK101(de)005:725: 'di dang rdzogs chen pas nyams rim bzhin mthun pa yin te /
NK101(de)005:726: dang po gnas pa'i nyams shes pa yul phyir mi 'phro bas rtse gcig tu thun thub /
NK101(de)005:727: g.yo ba'i nyams ting nge 'dzin la byings rgod sogs rkyen gyis mi gnod pas lo zlar gnas pa /
NK101(de)005:728: mnyam pa nyid kyi nyams mnyam gzhag la 'khor 'das la ro mnyam pas rjes shes la /
NK101(de)005:729: chos brgyad sgyu ma ltar khongs su chud nas 'jig pa bral ba /
NK101(de)005:730: lhun gyis grub pa'i nyams ting nge 'dzin thun mtshams las 'das pa rnams dang don gcig go //
NK101(de)005:731: 'di dag rgyas par ni yi ge mang por 'gro bas ma spros so //
NK101(de)005:732: gol sa dang skyon yon gyis gnas gal che ba
NK101(de)005:733: rnams ni snying tig gi mkha' 'gros zhus lan du
NK101(de)005:734: rgyas par gsungs pas der lta'o //
NK101(de)005:737: mi bsgom par reg pa rang lugs su zhog /
NK101(de)005:738: mi bsgom pas bsgom mi shes mi srid /
NK101(de)005:739: sems nyid rtog med du rig pa bsgom yin pas mi yong mi srid /
NK101(de)005:740: bsgom nyams kyi 'dod pa med pas gol mi srid /
NK101(de)005:743: rtog pa thams cad dngos por yang mi 'dzin /
NK101(de)005:744: stong par yang mi bsgom par 'dzin med ma bcos
NK101(de)005:745: pa'i ngang du rang sor bzhag pas 'chor sa dang
NK101(de)005:746: gol sa bya ba ci yang mi yong /
NK101(de)005:748: de ltar nyams su len pa gal che te /
NK101(de)005:750: bsgrub pa la gtso bor ma byas na mkhas btsun du barloma yang rtags kyi 'khrul pa mi sel /
NK101(de)005:751: sems la ting 'dzin ma skyes na go rtogs bzang yang rig pa las su mi rung /
NK101(de)005:752: rig pa las su ma rung na mi tshe chos la bskyal yang nam zhig tha mal du 'chi /
NK101(de)005:753: 'chi dus tha mal du shi na man ngag zab mo yod kyang bar dor rkyen ngan du 'gro /
NK101(de)005:755: nyams la chags na yang 'chings te /
NK101(de)005:757: nyams ni bsam gtan zhes bya bar gnas gong mar 'ching par byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin la /
NK101(de)005:758: rtog pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK101(de)005:759: pa bya ba 'khor ba gzhi med du grol bar
NK101(de)005:763: rnam rtog sgom du ma shar na //
NK101(de)005:765: bsgom chen bsgom gyis ma bcings na //
NK101(de)005:766: gzhan gyis bcings par mi nus pas //
NK101(de)005:767: go ba'i lta ba rgyab tu bor //
NK101(de)005:768: bsgom pa'i nyams myong smang nas bshig /
NK101(de)005:769: ces pa ltar nyams su blangs par bya /
NK101(de)005:770: da ni zhar byung du mkhas grub gong ma dag gi gsungs bsgros thor bu brjod par bya ste /
NK101(de)005:771: pan chen thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston gyis bka' las /
NK101(de)005:772: sems kyi gnas lugs ma bcos mtha' bzhi bral //
NK101(de)005:773: gang du'ang ma 'dzin yengs med rtse gcig ltos //
NK101(de)005:774: bde bsdug la sogs rtogs pa'i 'char sgo rnams //
NK101(de)005:775: chu bo'i brlabs bzhin dbyer med ngang du mnyam //
NK101(de)005:776: sna tshogs snang yang chu nang bza' skar bzhin //
NK101(de)005:777: shar dang ma shar ro gcig rtogs par gyis //
NK101(de)005:778: de ltar rtogs na bsgom du med pa'i don //
NK101(de)005:779: rgyun du goms pa bsgom pa chen po yin /
NK101(de)005:782: sems nyid ngo sprod pa'i rtogs pa snga ma 'gags /
NK101(de)005:784: da ltar gyis shes pa skyes la 'gag pa /
NK101(de)005:785: 'gag pa ma skyes pa hrig ge ba 'di rang yin no //
NK101(de)005:788: mnyam bzhag gi bsgom ni ma bcos pa yin la /
NK101(de)005:789: bsgom rgyu ni ye rang nas med /
NK101(de)005:790: lta stang ma shor tsam byas nas ni /
NK101(de)005:791: bsgom dang 'di mi bsgom med par rang lugs su bzhag go //
NK101(de)005:792: rjes kyis bsgom ni ma bcos pa la ngos bzungs te /
NK101(de)005:793: lus ngag yid gsum ched du brjod pa yengs pa
NK101(de)005:794: dang dga' mi dag'i rtogs pa thams cad ngos gzungs
NK101(de)005:795: gsungs kyang / rig pa dri ma med pa'i sgom pa la /
NK101(de)005:796: bsgom gyis zhen pa bor la thong /
NK101(de)005:797: mkhan po bskyur ba ni ma yengs par sgrims pa'i snying po ling gis bskyur ba yin /
NK101(de)005:799: yang gtol skyes kyis shes pa ngos gzungs dang /
NK101(de)005:800: dran pa rang dngas la 'gro yis gsungs /
NK101(de)005:802: pha rol tu phyin pa ni rten 'brel la sogs
NK101(de)005:803: pa lung dang rig pa'i sgo nas snang la rang
NK101(de)005:804: bzhin med pa gtan la phab nas bsgom pa yin
NK101(de)005:805: / mos pa stong nyid du byed pa yin te /
NK101(de)005:806: de dbu ma pa'i sgom lugs yin /
NK101(de)005:807: de rang yang bsgom bya bsgom byed dang bcas pa'i gnyis 'dzin gyi blor 'jug /
NK101(de)005:809: dngos po la gnod pa cung zhig rkyal bas sgrib
NK101(de)005:810: pa dpag tu med pa mdzad de sangs rgyas mi
NK101(de)005:811: nus / bka' gdams pa dang mtshan nyid pa thams cad de bsgom pa yin /
NK101(de)005:812: bla ma mi la'i lugs la /
NK101(de)005:813: mi dge ba bcu bsgom pas /
NK101(de)005:815: dge bcu bsgom pas lha mir 'khyam /
NK101(de)005:816: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro la chags nas bsgom pas lha tshe ring por skye /
NK101(de)005:817: dran pas zin pas rnam rtog ni yon tan /
NK101(de)005:818: ma zin pa la skyon du lta na de yang gnyis 'dzin gyis skyon /
NK101(de)005:819: rtogs med la sogs pa'i yon tan thams cad bsgrub par 'dod /
NK101(de)005:820: rnam rtog la sogs pa'i skyon thams cad spong bar 'dod na de yang gnyis 'dzin gyi skyon /
NK101(de)005:821: stong par bsgom kyang blo mi stong par bsgom kyang blo /
NK101(de)005:822: yod med du bsgom kyang blo /
NK101(de)005:823: mdor na bsgom tshad blo dang gnyis 'dzin las grol ba med gsungs /
NK101(de)005:824: rnam rtog byung na ji ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK101(de)005:825: de kha na gtsug tu bzhag pas chog /
NK101(de)005:828: pha rol tu phyin pa spong ba'i lam sa yin
NK101(de)005:829: pas mi sdug pa la sogs pa gnyen pos nyon
NK101(de)005:830: mongs pa ngo thug tu spong ba yin /
NK101(de)005:831: gsang sngags ni gzhi bsgyur ba'i lam yin pas dug lnga rnam rtog tu 'khyer ba yin /
NK101(de)005:832: dug lnga dang rnam rtog la dgag bsgrub gang yang ma byas par /
NK101(de)005:833: de khar tsug skyer gtsug pa rang gi rang zhir
NK101(de)005:834: 'gro ba yin no gsungs shing ji ltar mang ba
NK101(de)005:835: ltar me che ba yin rnam rtog ji ltar mang
NK101(de)005:836: ba ltar gnyis med kyis ye shes byas pa yin
NK101(de)005:837: pas dug lnga dang rnam rtog de ka ltar skyer
NK101(de)005:838: bcug pas chog / dgag sgrub med par ma bcos
NK101(de)005:839: pa 'di dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs
NK101(de)005:841: rang cag gi sangs rgyas ngo shes pa dang ma shes pa yang 'di ka yin no //
NK101(de)005:842: sangs rgyas la yang 'di ka las lhag pa med /
NK101(de)005:843: tshes gcig gi zla ba dang /
NK101(de)005:844: nya'i zla ba la zla ba tsam du khyad par med /
NK101(de)005:845: de bzhin du ma bcos par bzhag pas gnyis med
NK101(de)005:846: kyi ye shes rnal 'byor pas de ring rtogs pa
NK101(de)005:847: dang / sangs rgyas kyis thugs ye shes gnyis la gnyis med tsam du khyad par med /
NK101(de)005:848: gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rbad kyis chad tsa na sangs rgyas yin gsungs /
NK101(de)005:850: ma bcos pa la lo gcig bsgom pa rang gi mngon par shes pa 'ong ste gsung skad /
NK101(de)005:851: gzhan dag mi rtog pa du ma gcig la mnyam
NK101(de)005:852: bzhag byas nas rjes rmi lam sgyu ma ltar bsgom
NK101(de)005:853: pa yin / rje btsun gyi lugs kyi dug lnga
NK101(de)005:854: dang rnam rtog gnyis med kyi ye shes su khyer
NK101(de)005:855: nas gom tsa na thun mtshams med par thams cad
NK101(de)005:856: du mnyam bzhag 'ba' zhig tu 'khyer ba yin gsungs
NK101(de)005:857: pa yin / / dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK101(de)005:858: lho phyogs dpal gyi ri bor til+lo pas zhus pa
NK101(de)005:860: der mar la byon pas ma bcos pa'i don ma go nas /
NK101(de)005:861: yang zhur phyin pas mkha' 'gro ma sh+ri d+ha ra dang phrad nas /
NK101(de)005:862: rang gi sems la ma blta ma bsgom tha mal par zhog /
NK101(de)005:864: thog ma med pa nas da lta yan chad du
NK101(de)005:865: ma bcos pa snyug ma'i don nyin zhag phrug re'i
NK101(de)005:866: nang du yang yang skye yang ngo ma shes pas
NK101(de)005:867: lung ma bstan du song nas rang gzhan gyis don
NK101(de)005:868: ma grub gsungs / rje btsun khyi thul can gyi zhal nas /
NK101(de)005:869: chos nyid ma bcos pa la phogs gcig dran pas chog /
NK101(de)005:870: rtag tu stur re bya mi dgos /
NK101(de)005:871: dran pa de nas bor yang bor du mi btub pa 'ong gis /
NK101(de)005:873: rnam rtog tu 'dug rung 'jig rten pa'i rnam rtog min /
NK101(de)005:876: khong dang ma 'phrad tsa na nga ma bcos pa rang bsgom pa yin /
NK101(de)005:877: de rang du shes pas 'thums nas rtog med dar re las ma byung /
NK101(de)005:878: des na 'jig rten pa'i rang kha mar song /
NK101(de)005:879: khong gi de dgag bsgrub med pa'i gnyis med rang grol de go'o //
NK101(de)005:882: sems rang bzhin med pa bsgom pa de rang blor mi 'agro'am zhus pas /
NK101(de)005:883: sems rang bzhin med pas chu la chu thim mo /
NK101(de)005:884: rtag tu bsgom mi dgos te phogs cig dran pas chog gsungs /
NK101(de)005:885: bslod nas 'jog pa de rang blor mi 'agro'am zhus pas /
NK101(de)005:886: rang shugs kyi rtog med de sems gnas pa sha ma yin /
NK101(de)005:887: rtsa rlung la sogs pas rtog med dum re ba
NK101(de)005:888: de sems btsan bzung gi sems 'dzin bya ba yin
NK101(de)005:889: / sems gnas pa sha ma min no //
NK101(de)005:890: sems kho rang rtogs med du bade'am /
NK101(de)005:893: nyal ba la sogs pa'i spyod lam gang bder bzhag go /
NK101(de)005:894: dgag bsgrub stsol ba gang yang mi bya bar mi rtogs par 'dug kyang rung /
NK101(de)005:895: rnam rtog sna tshogs su 'dug kyang rung /
NK101(de)005:896: ma bcos par bzhag pa rang gi gnyis 'dzin dang bral /
NK101(de)005:897: gnyis med kyi ye shes rang shar bar 'dug ang
NK101(de)005:898: snyam pa'i go ba byung tsa na sems kho rang
NK101(de)005:899: gi ngo bo'o // gshis sam 'dug tshul shes pa yin /
NK101(de)005:900: de ltar go na bsgom bya mi dgos /
NK101(de)005:901: bor ba'am bzhag tu mi btub par bsgom dbang med du skye ba yin gsungs /
NK101(de)005:902: sems kyi ngo bo shes pa ji lta bu lags zhus pas /
NK101(de)005:903: ma bcos pa la ma bcos par shes pa de ka ngo bo shes pa yin gsungs /
NK101(de)005:904: ma bcos par bzhag pas dgag sgrub kyi bya rgyu
NK101(de)005:905: dang bral nas gnyis med kyi ye shes rang 'char
NK101(de)005:906: ba de ni mi rtog pa yin /
NK101(de)005:907: lkugs ma bu ram mur ba'am gzhon nu ma 'dod
NK101(de)005:908: chags kyi bde ba myong ba ltar smra ru med
NK101(de)005:910: ye shes gsal ba de ni gsal ba yin no //
NK101(de)005:911: mi rtog pa dang gsal ba byung tsa na gnyis 'dzin gyi bya rgyu thams cad 'gags nas 'gro /
NK101(de)005:914: de ltar bde ba gsal ba mi rtog pa gsum
NK101(de)005:915: gyis phan yon mthong chos tshe 'di la 'byung ngo
NK101(de)005:916: // 'jig rten pa'i rnam rtog rang ga ma dang /
NK101(de)005:917: rnal 'byor pas ngo shes pas rnam rtog gnyis kyi khyad ngo shes ma shes la /
NK101(de)005:918: bsgom nas shes na rtog par 'gyur ma bsgom par
NK101(de)005:919: shes na rang grol du mi 'gyur ram byas na
NK101(de)005:920: brtugs nas 'gro ba'i rgad po de 'dra nga'i rtsar
NK101(de)005:921: byung gsungs / pan chen sh+aakya sh+ris kyang /
NK101(de)005:922: cir snang rang sor bzhag na bya bral lhun gyis grub /
NK101(de)005:923: gang shar ngo yis bzung na rig pa rang sar grol /
NK101(de)005:924: 'gyu ba'i rtsad rjes bcad na dran rtog dbyings su yal /
NK101(de)005:925: thun mtshams dran pas bzung na mnyam rjes ro gcig 'grub /
NK101(de)005:928: nyon mongs bkag pas ma khegs tshe /
NK101(de)005:929: gdams ngag rgyal po sor bzhag byung /
NK101(de)005:930: ngang la bzhag pas dbyings su yal /
NK101(de)005:931: blang dor bya ba'i ming yang med /
NK101(de)005:933: rgyal ba yang dgon pas ye bsgom la blo yis ma bsgom mdzod /
NK101(de)005:934: rang babs la gzo yis ma bcos mdzod /
NK101(de)005:935: bsgom bsting gsal la rkyen gyi sgyur du med kyis /
NK101(de)005:936: blo rtogs pa la skyon du ma blta bar /
NK101(de)005:937: mi rtog par ched du ma bsgom par /
NK101(de)005:938: sems rang lugs su zhog la rgyang so tshugs /
NK101(de)005:939: bsgom zhi gnas kyi mthil du phebs pa gcig 'ong gi sems ngos bzung med pa stong pa'i dbyings /
NK101(de)005:940: 'gag med du gsal ba rig pa'i sgo /
NK101(de)005:941: blo bral gyi gsal stong rjen pa 'di la rang sor bzhag gin ngang la ltos dang /
NK101(de)005:942: bsgom lhag mthong gi rang ngo mthong ba gcig 'ong gi /
NK101(de)005:943: ma yengs pa'i dran pa so ma shor /
NK101(de)005:944: ma bsgom pa'i gnas lugs gzo ma byas /
NK101(de)005:945: bsam med kyi rig pa smra ma 'dod /
NK101(de)005:946: rtag chad kyi ma slad kha yan du skyong dang /
NK101(de)005:947: bsgom spros bral gyi ma bu 'phrad pa gcig 'ong gi /
NK101(de)005:948: blo rtogs pa 'gyu ba gnas lugs kyis sgo /
NK101(de)005:949: rang ngo shes pa nyams len gyi gnad /
NK101(de)005:952: rtog pa 'phro ba de tshur dkug nas bsgom la 'jog pa ni min /
NK101(de)005:953: rtog pa ral me ba de ka'i ngo bo la lta ba yin no //
NK101(de)005:954: rtog pa dang bsgom gnyis la ngo shes ma shes min pa khyad med do //
NK101(de)005:955: gnas pa'i dus dang 'gyu ba'i dus gnyis la sems kyi ngo bo gcig las 'dug go ltos dang /
NK101(de)005:958: ma bcos pa'i shes pa ngos 'dzin pa la ma
NK101(de)005:959: bcos par 'jog pa 'di ka zab pa yin gsungs
NK101(de)005:960: / bzung dran gyis dus su mig gis gzugs mthong
NK101(de)005:961: pas rang ngo shes pa'i gsal le hrig ge ba
NK101(de)005:962: de rang la mnyam par bzhag pa rang gis dus
NK101(de)005:963: / su yang / gzugs kyi byed pa las 'phros pa'i 'char sgo mang dag gcig /
NK101(de)005:964: dron pa'i khrod nas 'gyu ba'i grogs kho rang gi byed kyi yod de kho rang gis mi tshor /
NK101(de)005:965: rang gi gdong pa rang gis mi mthong ba dang 'dra /
NK101(de)005:966: sgra dang dri la sogs pa la'ang 'agre'o //
NK101(de)005:967: de thams cad kyi rgyu mtshan sems dang dran pa
NK101(de)005:968: la 'dres par yul yul can du bzung nas yod
NK101(de)005:969: pas lan / rang gsal gyis dran pa'i dus su
NK101(de)005:970: tshogs drug gis snang pa thams cad rang rang so
NK101(de)005:971: sor blta bya blta byed dang bral ba'i shes bya
NK101(de)005:972: shes byed kyis gnyis 'dzin med pa rang rig cing
NK101(de)005:974: gzung bran de rtsol med kyis dran par 'pho ba'i
NK101(de)005:975: thabs la'ang gzung dran la brtson 'grus bskyed pa kho
NK101(de)005:977: bzung dran gyis dran pa brtan po yod na 'ang dus der lam du song ba yin /
NK101(de)005:978: lam du 'gro ba skyon med gcig la gang shar
NK101(de)005:979: rang rig rang gsal du 'char dgos pas brtsol med
NK101(de)005:981: gzung dran la yul yul can gyis dran pa las med gsungs /
NK101(de)005:982: yang tha mal shes pa rang ga 'di /
NK101(de)005:983: ma bsgom chos kyis sku ru shar /
NK101(de)005:984: sangs rgyas rang gi sems las snyed /
NK101(de)005:988: bsgom zhes byas kyang bsgom rgyu brdul tsam med /
NK101(de)005:989: bsgom med byas kyang yengs su skad gcig med /
NK101(de)005:990: don mthong ba la bsgom du bsgom mkhan med //
NK101(de)005:991: blo rtog can la yengs su skad gcig med //
NK101(de)005:992: bsgom med yengs med rnal 'byor bsgoms pa yin //
NK101(de)005:993: rtogs ldan sems la 'chos rgyu ci yang med //
NK101(de)005:995: snang ba mi spong stong pa mi bsgom shing //
NK101(de)005:996: rnam rtog mi 'gegs rtog med mi bsgom mo //
NK101(de)005:997: gal te de ltar sgoms na yang pa yin //
NK101(de)005:998: blo la dran snang mtshan ma ci shar yang //
NK101(de)005:999: dran snang de kha chos nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)005:1000: cer gyi bltas pas rang sar grol bar 'gyur //
NK101(de)005:1001: de la gnyen pos bcos bsgyur bya mi dgos //
NK101(de)005:1005: spangs gnyen gnyis med rang grol te //
NK101(de)005:1006: 'khrul pa dag pas ye shes lags //
NK101(de)005:1008: 'di yin med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK101(de)005:1009: 'di bsgom med pa lam gyis gnad //
NK101(de)005:1010: bya byed bral ba gnyug ma'i sems //
NK101(de)005:1011: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'od gsal lags //
NK101(de)005:1013: sems 'dzin pa bas kyang stong pa zab //
NK101(de)005:1014: sems bzung ba yod na gang 'gror thong //
NK101(de)005:1015: don bsgom pa yod na bslod las zhog /
NK101(de)005:1016: de gsung rab kun gyi snying por 'dug /
NK101(de)005:1017: dpal ldan bla ma rnams kyis phyag bzhes lags //
NK101(de)005:1018: bsgom ma yengs pas kyang yeng pa zab //
NK101(de)005:1019: bsgom yengs med yod na yengs la bor //
NK101(de)005:1020: nyams gdam pa bas kyang gang byung zab //
NK101(de)005:1021: nyams gdams pa zhog la gang byung gyis //
NK101(de)005:1022: rlung 'dzin pa bas kyang rgya yan zab //
NK101(de)005:1023: rlung bzung ba yod na yan du chug /
NK101(de)005:1024: lus 'khrul 'khor bas kyang bde ba zab //
NK101(de)005:1025: lus 'khrul 'khor yod na shig la thong //
NK101(de)005:1026: gzer 'pho 'chug med na thebs pa yin //
NK101(de)005:1027: blo phyogs zhen med na dbu ma yin //
NK101(de)005:1029: ma yengs ting 'dzin yengs su bcug na 'char //
NK101(de)005:1030: mi rtogs ting 'dzin rtogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK101(de)005:1031: blo bur nyon mongs gnyugs ma'i ye shes yin //
NK101(de)005:1032: bsgoms na blo yin yengs na 'khrul pa ste //
NK101(de)005:1033: blo nyid blo 'das 'khrul pa ye shes so //
NK101(de)005:1034: ji ltar bsgoms kyang bsgom gyis ma gos shing //
NK101(de)005:1035: gang ltar byas kyang byed pa kun dang bral //
NK101(de)005:1036: gnyis su bzung ba yang gnyis 'dzin ma mchis shing //
NK101(de)005:1037: mang por snang yang gcig gi ngang tshul can //
NK101(de)005:1038: gcig blo de ni bsam pa'i yul las 'das //
NK101(de)005:1039: ji ltar bsam kyang gzo med rang grol yin //
NK101(de)005:1041: snubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtshos //
NK101(de)005:1042: sems dang ches ni ci yang ma yin pas //
NK101(de)005:1043: bsgom pa'i tshe na ci yang mi bsgom mo //
NK101(de)005:1044: rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma ci byung yang //
NK101(de)005:1045: rtogs pa de nyid chos nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)005:1046: chos kyi dbyings nyid gzhan du bsgom mi dgos //
NK101(de)005:1047: de la gnyen pos bcos shing dgag tu med //
NK101(de)005:1048: 'di ltar dus gsum rnam pa thams cad du //
NK101(de)005:1049: nyid las ma yongs pa ni chos kyis sku //
NK101(de)005:1051: bsgom dang bsgom par bya ba gnyis med par //
NK101(de)005:1052: don dam ngang las bde bar gnas pa ni //
NK101(de)005:1053: byang chub sems bsgom zhes kyang de la bya //
NK101(de)005:1055: de ltar mdo rgyud bstan bcos rnams dang /
NK101(de)005:1056: grub chen rnams kyis mgur na mang du yod de 'dir thor bu las bri bar ma nus la /
NK101(de)005:1057: re res kyang ngo 'phrod shing nges shes rnyed pa'i dgos pa yod de //
NK101(de)005:1058: lce bsgom chen po shes rab rdo rjes /
NK101(de)005:1059: chos kyi rtogs par bya rgyu sems las med kyang /
NK101(de)005:1060: ngo sprod gdams ngag med na rtogs par dka' bas /
NK101(de)005:1061: grub thob rnams kyi gsung la nan tan bskyed cig /
NK101(de)005:1063: de lta bu'i don dang mi ldan na /
NK101(de)005:1065: sems kyi gsang 'di ma rig na //
NK101(de)005:1067: bde ba 'dod pa tsam gyi las //
NK101(de)005:1068: de ni ngal ba kho nar zad ces dang /
NK101(de)005:1070: snang stong sems kyi 'dug tshul ma shes na /
NK101(de)005:1071: 'phral snang rig pa rno yang log shes yin /
NK101(de)005:1073: de bas na snying po'i lam 'dir 'bad pa gal che ste /
NK101(de)005:1074: jo bo chen po rjes bden gnyis las /
NK101(de)005:1075: tshe 'di yun thung shes bya'i rnam pa mang //
NK101(de)005:1076: tshe yi tshad kyang ji tsam mi shes pas //
NK101(de)005:1077: ngang pas chu las 'o ma len pa ltar //
NK101(de)005:1078: gang la gces pa de ni len par bya //
NK101(de)005:1081: mi snying can kun rang la phyi thag srings //
NK101(de)005:1082: rang mi slu na snying nas chos gcig gyis //
NK101(de)005:1083: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'bung dgos so //
NK101(de)005:1084: lam bsgom pa'i tshul gsal bar bstan zin to //
NK101(de)005:1085: da ni spyod pa ston te /
NK101(de)005:1086: seng ge lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1087: bung ba lta bu'i spyod pa la sogs pa mang du gsungs kyang /
NK101(de)005:1088: spyod pa'i ngo bo chos kyi grogs su 'gro ba zhig dgos pa yin /
NK101(de)005:1089: de la brtan pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa dag
NK101(de)005:1090: la ni spyod pa blang dor dang bral ba yin
NK101(de)005:1091: la / gsar bu ba dag gis kyang spyod lam
NK101(de)005:1092: 'gro 'chag nyal 'dug thams cad du dran pa dang
NK101(de)005:1094: de ltar mi ldan na bsgom skye dus mi yong
NK101(de)005:1095: ste dam pas nya ma dge 'dun bskyid la gsungs
NK101(de)005:1096: pa bzhin no // mtshan mo rmi lam gzungs ba'i thabs la rtsal sbyangs te /
NK101(de)005:1098: nyin mo'i nga tshe 'di'i bya brel gyis g.yengs pas khyer bas na gnad che sa yin /
NK101(de)005:1099: de ltar nyin mtshan kun tu ci byed sgom dang
NK101(de)005:1100: ma bral bar bya ste mi tshe stong zad la
NK101(de)005:1101: mi btang / dran pa dang ma bral ba'i spyod
NK101(de)005:1102: pa 'di ni mnyam bzhag las myur ba ches zab
NK101(de)005:1103: mi btang / ste / bla ma zhang rin po ches /
NK101(de)005:1104: mnyam bzhag dus kyis mnyam bzhag ste /
NK101(de)005:1105: mnyam bzhag ma yin rjes thob yin //
NK101(de)005:1106: rjes thob dus kyi rjes thob de //
NK101(de)005:1107: rjes thob ma yin mnyam bzhag yin //
NK101(de)005:1109: zhar la las rgyu 'bras phra zhing phra ba la'ang 'dzems dgos te /
NK101(de)005:1111: nga lta ba nam mkha' bas kyang mtho /
NK101(de)005:1112: rgyu 'bras bag phye bas kyang zhib /
NK101(de)005:1114: thun mgor skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed rgya chen po bya zhing /
NK101(de)005:1115: thun mtshams su bdag gis dge rtsa sems can thams cad sangs rgyas thob pa'i rgyur bsngo'o //
NK101(de)005:1116: 'di dang mi ldan na lta ba mtho bas mi phan te /
NK101(de)005:1117: theg pa dman pa'i lam du gol /
NK101(de)005:1118: 'dus byas kyi dge ba khyad du mi bsad /
NK101(de)005:1119: bla ma ci gsung gi bka' mi bcag /
NK101(de)005:1120: lus longs spyod thams cad bla ma la 'bul zhing
NK101(de)005:1121: mos gus 'chi ma 'khrug pa ma byung bar du
NK101(de)005:1123: gsang sngags pa lam zab mo bla ma'i lam bya
NK101(de)005:1124: ba nyams myong dang rtog pa dang yon tan thams
NK101(de)005:1125: cad bla ma'i byin brlabs la brten nas 'byung pas
NK101(de)005:1126: gnad shin tu zab pa yin /
NK101(de)005:1127: chos dang mi mthun pa'i grogs dang mi 'grogs yon
NK101(de)005:1128: tan skye dus rang mthong mi bya bar kun la
NK101(de)005:1129: dag snang sbyangs / bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa'i thabs su gyur pa na /
NK101(de)005:1130: gang yin yang zhum pa med par rtson pas dang du blangs /
NK101(de)005:1131: dam tshig dang sdom pa sna gcig dang ma nyams par bsrung /
NK101(de)005:1132: gal te nyams na gshags pa dang phyir bcos la sogs pas sor chud par bya'o //
NK101(de)005:1133: mdor na rnam pa thams cad du /
NK101(de)005:1134: tha mal shes pa sor bzhag la /
NK101(de)005:1135: ngo shes byed pa ma gtogs pa /
NK101(de)005:1136: bsgom rgyu gzhan med bsgom chen tsho /
NK101(de)005:1137: zhes rje sgam po pas gsungs pa ltar spyod do //
NK101(de)005:1138: de ltar yang ni gu ma sngon 'gro la gtso bor byed /
NK101(de)005:1139: mee tri pa dngos gzhi la gtso bor byed /
NK101(de)005:1140: su kha sid+hi rjes la gtso bor byed /
NK101(de)005:1142: lam 'di skyong ba'i gang zag de yang rjes la gtso bor byed pa zab pa yin no //
NK101(de)005:1143: spyod pa'i tshul bstan zin to //
NK101(de)005:1144: da ni de ltar nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu bshad par bya ste /
NK101(de)005:1145: rang gi sems gdod nas dag cing lhun gyis grub pa de nyid /
NK101(de)005:1147: rnam rtog bden pa ma yin pas rin chen sems ni dri mar byas /
NK101(de)005:1148: ji ltar nam mkha' 'jig med bzhin /
NK101(de)005:1149: dag pa'i sems ni dag par 'gyur /
NK101(de)005:1150: rin chen sems ni rab bskul bas //
NK101(de)005:1151: ji ltar nam mkha' de bzhin sems //
NK101(de)005:1152: skye 'dir sangs rgyas mchog nyid du //
NK101(de)005:1153: sems bsgom pas ni sangs rgya'o //
NK101(de)005:1155: 'khrul pa blo bur bas sgrib pas bag chags thams
NK101(de)005:1156: cad ma spangs dbyings su dag nas mngon du gyur
NK101(de)005:1157: pa de la chos sku dag pa gnyis ldan zhes
NK101(de)005:1158: bya / rdo rje zam pa dag blo'i mtha' zab
NK101(de)005:1159: cing cha phra ba yang mi gnas pa dbyer mi
NK101(de)005:1160: phyed pa'i dus zhes pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1161: rdzogs chen pa gzhan dag ni 'bras bu bzhi la rdzogs pa zhes 'dod de /
NK101(de)005:1163: sems rang bzhin gyis dag pa la dri ma blo
NK101(de)005:1164: bur bas sgrib pa'i 'khrul pa'i snang sa ma spangs
NK101(de)005:1165: gnas su dag pas de la sangs rgyas chos kyi
NK101(de)005:1166: sku zhes bya'o // 'di la rje btsun chen pos /
NK101(de)005:1167: rang bzhin rgyu la bsam na lhun grub ste /
NK101(de)005:1168: mtha' yas tshogs ni gnas 'gyur yin /
NK101(de)005:1169: des na lhun grub gnas 'gyur mi 'gal ba /
NK101(de)005:1170: 'di ni 'bras bu'i 'khor 'das dbyer med yin ces gsungs so //
NK101(de)005:1171: sku 'di ni rnam par rtog pa thams cad bral
NK101(de)005:1172: ba stong gsal bde ba chen po'i ngang la dbyings
NK101(de)005:1173: dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par gnas shing snang
NK101(de)005:1174: ba yin la / de nyid gzhan gyis mi mthong yang /
NK101(de)005:1175: rang nyams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la snang ba yin te /
NK101(de)005:1178: sangs rgyas chos kyi sku ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi ngo gang la snang ngo //
NK101(de)005:1180: kha gcig chos sku zhal phyag med pa nam mkha' lta bu'i stong pa la bzhed kyang /
NK101(de)005:1182: 'khor bar rnam par rtog pa zad pa yang rnam par dag pa ste /
NK101(de)005:1183: sangs rgyas rnams kyis yang dag pa'i sku de ni med pa ma yin no //
NK101(de)005:1186: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur la /
NK101(de)005:1187: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnam mi rtogs /
NK101(de)005:1188: 'gro grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad du /
NK101(de)005:1189: 'di ni spros dang bral ba snang pa yin /
NK101(de)005:1192: ye shes kyi rang bzhin can gyi sku shes bya'i
NK101(de)005:1193: bud shing skam po ma lus pa bsregs pa las
NK101(de)005:1194: / shes bya skye ba med pa la skye ba
NK101(de)005:1195: dang ldan par gyur pa gang yin pa de ni
NK101(de)005:1196: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos kyi sku'o //
NK101(de)005:1197: zhes pas gsal ba yin la /
NK101(de)005:1199: thogs ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)005:1200: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa yod /
NK101(de)005:1201: zhes pa dag tshul mtshungs pa yin no //
NK101(de)005:1202: de ltar mtshan ma dang spros pa ci yang mi mnga' ba dbyings kyis sku de'i ngang las /
NK101(de)005:1203: gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba'i sku mched pa ni /
NK101(de)005:1204: 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtog pa med kyang /
NK101(de)005:1205: sngon gyis smon lam gyi mthu dang /
NK101(de)005:1206: rang bzhin gyi yon tan gyi stobs kyi rgyu las /
NK101(de)005:1207: gdul bya'i rkyen dang 'phrad pa na /
NK101(de)005:1208: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang sprul pa'i skur /
NK101(de)005:1209: snang ba la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK101(de)005:1210: kyi sgyu ma chu dang zla ba lta bu ni
NK101(de)005:1212: chu dang nam mkha'i zla gzugs bzhin /
NK101(de)005:1214: de ltar yang rtog pa med pa de'i ngang las
NK101(de)005:1215: 'gro ba'i don gang la gang 'dul du mdzad pa
NK101(de)005:1216: ni / dper na nor bu dang dpag bsam shing
NK101(de)005:1217: dang bum pa bzang po la sogs pa la gzhan
NK101(de)005:1218: gyi re ba bskong mnyam pa'i rtog pa med kyang
NK101(de)005:1219: ni / / rang bzhin gyi grub pas nus mthu 'gro ba'i re ba skongs pa ltar yin te /
NK101(de)005:1221: yid bzhin nor bu dpag bsam shing /
NK101(de)005:1222: ji ltar re ba yongs skong ba /
NK101(de)005:1223: de bzhin gdul bya'i smon lam gyi /
NK101(de)005:1224: dbang gi rgyal ba'i sku snang ngo //
NK101(de)005:1227: yid bzhin nor bu dpag bsam shing bzhin du /
NK101(de)005:1228: smon lam dbang gis re ba yongs skongs ba /
NK101(de)005:1229: de ni 'jig rten tha snyad kun rdzob te /
NK101(de)005:1230: dam pa'i don du 'ga' yang yod ma yin //
NK101(de)005:1232: de la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i ngo bo ni /
NK101(de)005:1234: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis ldan /
NK101(de)005:1235: dpe byad brgyad bcu'i bdag nyid de /
NK101(de)005:1236: theg chen nye bar longs spyod phyir /
NK101(de)005:1237: thub pa'i longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhed /
NK101(de)005:1239: sku des byang chub sems dpa' sa thob pa rnams kyi don mdzad pa yin te /
NK101(de)005:1241: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni sa la gnas pa'i
NK101(de)005:1242: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi ngo gang la snang
NK101(de)005:1244: sprul pa'i sku ni chos kyi sku cir yang mi
NK101(de)005:1245: 'dzin pa'i ngang nas sems can gyi snang ngor gang
NK101(de)005:1246: la gang 'dul du snang bar mdzad pa ni rgyud
NK101(de)005:1247: bla ma las / chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par /
NK101(de)005:1248: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis /
NK101(de)005:1249: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang /
NK101(de)005:1251: mngon rtogs rgyan las gzo dang skye ba byang chub che /
NK101(de)005:1253: ngo bo ni de nyid las /
NK101(de)005:1254: gang gis srid pa ji srid par /
NK101(de)005:1255: 'gro la phan pa sna tshogs dag /
NK101(de)005:1256: mnyam du mdzad pa'i sku de na /
NK101(de)005:1257: thub pa'i sprul sku rgyun mi chad /
NK101(de)005:1260: gzos 'dul ba la byi shwa kar+m+ma lta bu dang /
NK101(de)005:1261: skye pas 'dul ba la sems can gyi gnas rigs sna tshogs pa /
NK101(de)005:1262: skye ba bzhes pa skyes rab las bshad pa lta bu dang /
NK101(de)005:1263: byang chub chen po sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1264: thub pa drug la sogs par sprul nas gang la gang 'dul du 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK101(de)005:1265: sku des ni 'gro ba rang rgyud pa dag gi don mdzad pa ste /
NK101(de)005:1268: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku ni byis pa so so skye bo rnams kyi ngo gang la snang ngo //
NK101(de)005:1270: 'dir rnying ma dag sprul sku thub pa drug ces bzhed pa la /
NK101(de)005:1272: 'o na thub pa gzhan lnga yi /
NK101(de)005:1273: mdzad pa bcu gnyis gang du spyad /
NK101(de)005:1274: chos kyi 'khor lo gang du bskor /
NK101(de)005:1275: zhes sogs rgol ba ni rang nyid thos pa chung par zad de /
NK101(de)005:1277: rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud las /
NK101(de)005:1278: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes brnyes nas thams cad
NK101(de)005:1279: mkhyen pa'i ye shes de sems can thams cad la
NK101(de)005:1280: rnam par phye ste tshul sna tshogs dang /
NK101(de)005:1282: thabs sna tshogs dbang gis ston cing /
NK101(de)005:1283: kha gcig la ni nyan thos kyis theg pa'i tshul /
NK101(de)005:1284: kha gcig la ni nyos kyi theg pa'i tshul /
NK101(de)005:1285: kha gcig la ni theg pa chen po'i tshul /
NK101(de)005:1286: kha gcig la ni mngon par shes pa lnga'i tshul /
NK101(de)005:1287: kha gcig la ni lhar skye ba bya ba dang /
NK101(de)005:1288: kha gcig la ni mir skye bar bya ba dang /
NK101(de)005:1289: ji tsam du lto 'phye chen po dang /
NK101(de)005:1295: mi'am cir skye bar bya ba'i bar du chos ston pa lags so //
NK101(de)005:1296: de la sems can la sangs rgyas kyi 'dul bar
NK101(de)005:1297: bya ba dag gi ni sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su
NK101(de)005:1298: mthong / la las ni nyos kyi gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1299: la las ni rang sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1300: la las kyi byang chub sems pa'i gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1301: la las ni dbang phyug chen po'i gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1302: la las ni tshang pa'i gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1303: la las ni sred med kyi bu'i gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1304: la las ni rnam thos kyi bu'i gzugs su mthong /
NK101(de)005:1305: la las ni lto 'phye chen po'i dang /
NK101(de)005:1306: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i bar du mthong ste /
NK101(de)005:1307: rang gi tshig brjod pa'i tshul dag dang /
NK101(de)005:1308: spyod lam sna tshogs su snang par mthong ngo //
NK101(de)005:1309: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes de yang 'di ltar
NK101(de)005:1310: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par 'phro ba'i ror cig
NK101(de)005:1311: pa lags so // zhes pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1313: gang du snang nas kyang sems can gyis don mdzad do //
NK101(de)005:1314: chang tshong mar snang nas kyang sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK101(de)005:1315: seng ger snang nas sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK101(de)005:1316: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas na /
NK101(de)005:1317: sems can so so rang rang gi mos pa dang mthun par /
NK101(de)005:1319: lha ma yin la thags bzang rigs dang /
NK101(de)005:1320: mi la sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1321: byol song la seng ge rab brtan dang /
NK101(de)005:1322: yi dwags la nam mkha' mdzod dam kha 'bar ma /
NK101(de)005:1323: dmyal ba la chos kyi rgyal po gshin rje'i bar
NK101(de)005:1324: du snang nas brda' dang thabs mkhas pas spyod lam
NK101(de)005:1325: sna tshogs pa dag gis rim gyi chos kyi snod
NK101(de)005:1326: rung du mdzad pa gong gi lung gi bsgrubs zin
NK101(de)005:1327: to // de ltar sku gcig tu 'dod pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1328: de bzhin du gnyis pa dang /
NK101(de)005:1332: de dag kyang sku gsum du mi 'du ba med
NK101(de)005:1333: pas na cung zad tsam gcig bshad pa yin no
NK101(de)005:1334: // rgyas par 'dod na gzhan du blta bar bya'o //
NK101(de)005:1335: de lta bur sems kyis lam la goms par bya
NK101(de)005:1336: ba 'di ni chos thams cad kyi don nyams su
NK101(de)005:1337: len par byed pa yin te /
NK101(de)005:1341: ji bzhin rtogs pa mngon pa ste //
NK101(de)005:1342: rnam rtog gcod phyir gcod yin la //
NK101(de)005:1343: sdug bsngal zhi phyir zhi byed yin //
NK101(de)005:1344: 'dzin pa sbyong bas blo sbyongs yin //
NK101(de)005:1345: mthar 'dzin zhi bas dbu ma'i lam //
NK101(de)005:1346: rang grol kun khyab phyag rgya che //
NK101(de)005:1347: ngang la rdzogs pas rdzogs chen yin //
NK101(de)005:1349: shes rab zhan pas rmongs pa bdag lta bus /
NK101(de)005:1350: nges don bstan la dbab par mi nus shing /
NK101(de)005:1351: lta ba'i gdeng dang bsgom pa'i nyams myong med //
NK101(de)005:1352: sbyangs pa'i shes rgya chen po'ang ma mchis kyang /
NK101(de)005:1353: rdo rje 'chang dngos bla chen chos kyi rje'i //
NK101(de)005:1354: thugs rje'i byin rlabs snying la cung zad babs //
NK101(de)005:1355: de phyir bla ma sh+aakya bzang po yis //
NK101(de)005:1356: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rnam dbye dgos so ces //
NK101(de)005:1357: nan gyi bskul ba'i ngo ru bris pa 'di //
NK101(de)005:1358: legs par rtags la nyams su blangs par mdzod //
NK101(de)005:1359: gang dag 'di la nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK101(de)005:1360: de nyid gzigs pa'i skyes chen rnams la gshags //
NK101(de)005:1361: bod 'gyur bka' dang bstan bcos grangs mang zhing //
NK101(de)005:1362: gdams ngag so sor zab pa'ang bsam las 'das //
NK101(de)005:1363: tshul bzhin nyams su len pa'i gang zag nyung //
NK101(de)005:1364: de phyir bdag 'dra'i brtsom pas ci zhig bya //
NK101(de)005:1365: de ltar na yang 'dir 'bad dge ba gang //
NK101(de)005:1366: rtogs bral ma bcos rang babs de bzhin nyid //
NK101(de)005:1367: bde gshegs dgongs don rtogs pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK101(de)005:1368: 'gro rnams kun tu bzang po'i sar 'god shog //
NK101(de)005:1369: byang chub sems kyi don bsgom pa'i yi ge gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don gsal ba zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)005:1370: kahthog bla ma sh+aakya bzang pos nan tan du skul ba'i ngor /
NK101(de)005:1371: lha rje blo gros bzang po'i gtsang rong gi ri khrod du bris pa'o //
NK101(de)005:1372: 'di kyang sems can thams cad kyi rgyud las blo
NK101(de)005:1373: bral zag pa med pa'i ye shes mngon du 'char
